===========================
cryptonium: Crypto library
===========================

.. image:: https://github.com/piper-hq/cryptonium/actions/workflows/build.yml/badge.svg
  :alt: Build
  :target: https://github.com/piper-hq/cryptonium/actions/workflows/build.yml
